modules.description: Generates and updates table of contents in Markdown files by parsing headers and restructuring links. Processes strings and file contents, extracting and reordering section titles and anchors. Updates existing TOC blocks with accurate, nested links based on header hierarchy.

Generates and manipulates table of contents from Markdown documents using Omd's parsing and rendering capabilities. Processes `Omd.doc` to extract and format structured navigation data, supporting depth control and link insertion. Outputs a string representation or a pretty-printed version of the table of contents.
